{
  "stem": "11272.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I-- when I told her-- told this officer that, they brought her in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And, and she says, no, I've never seen this bastard, [LAUGHS] you know, at, at me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I described their home, described their pig, described everything about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And of course, quite frankly, a few days later, I was in good enough shape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my two brothers and I got on the first truck, American truck, that took people back to the Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Because we were more interested than anything else to find our family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We still had hopes that mother and father were alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we got to Prague, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And lo and behold, a miracle did happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We found our brother, Ben.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was working for the owner as a driver and attached to the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had an apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he took us to his apartment and fed us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got us some clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And more than anything else, he told us that another brother-- when he was liberated by the Russians and he joined the Russian forces, he saw our brother, Bernie.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a couple weeks later, Bernie shows up, with his girlfriend, who was nice-- wife, for over, over 50 years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he told us our brother, Philip, was alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He also was liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were in the Hungarian forced-labor camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's the oldest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we got word that he was getting-- going to get married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because his girlfriend was liberated in Belsen-Bergen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they are going to get married.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went back to our village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And lo and behold, we were there, celebrating the wedding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, we were resigned to the fact that our parents were not alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But meanwhile, we found our sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
